**Edit A — `@theme inline` block:** Add new Tailwind color utility mappings alongside the existing ones. These map Tailwind class names (`bg-sidebar`, `text-sidebar-foreground`, etc.) to the corresponding CSS custom properties that the theme hook will set on `:root` via `style.setProperty`.

