**Edit C — `@variant dark` fallback overrides (inside the existing `@variant dark { ... }` block):** Mirror the above but with dark-mode-appropriate fallbacks.

```css
    --sidebar: color-mix(in srgb, var(--background) 96%, var(--color-white));
    --sidebar-foreground: var(--color-neutral-300);
    --sidebar-accent: --alpha(var(--color-white) / 6%);
    --sidebar-accent-foreground: var(--foreground);
